            <div class="section">
                <div class="container is-large single_fatwa">

                    <div class="single-layout__title has-text-centered">
                        <h1 class="title is-4 is-size-5-touch" >
                            Meaning of “being with” in the verse “And whoso obeys Allah and the Messenger , then they will be with those on whom Allah has bestowed His Grace, of the Prophets, the Siddiqoon , the martyrs, and the righteous... [an-Nisa’ 4:69]
                        </h1>
                    </div>

                    <div class="single-layout__meta no-print layout-section  ">
        <div class="level is-mobile">
            <div class="level-left">

                
                <div class="level-item has-separator is-hidden-mobile">
                    <p class="subtitle has-text-muted has-title-case">
                        Publication : 29-09-2016
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="level-item has-separator is-hidden-mobile">
                    <p class="subtitle has-text-muted has-title-case">
                        Views :

                                                    102627
                                            </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="level-right _mr--2">
                
                <div class="level-item">

        <div class="dropdown lang-dropdown is-small is-right is-hoverable">
            <div class="dropdown-trigger">
                <button class="button has-shadow" aria-haspopup="true">
                    <span class="is-uppercase">en</span>
                    <span class="icon is-large">
                    <i class="icon-angle-down fa-lg"></i>
